These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: plum, peach
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | fanta |
| Food       | plum | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | 7up |
| Sport      | lacrosse     | baseball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, family
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
1. the australian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the australian is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family  |
| Nationality   | australian | indian |

 #################################

 
