The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, dressmaker
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Job     | project-manager        | dressmaker |

