1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | puzzles |
| Sport   | sailing | cricket   |

 